javadoc:
Interface for a Register Change set.  Objects that implements this interface track
 various change information on a set of addresses where the program register values have changed.

methods.name: addRegisterRange
methods.comment: Adds the ranges of addresses that have register changes.

params.name: addr1
params.comment: the first address in the range.

params.name: addr2
params.comment: the last address in the range.

methods.javadoc: Returns the set of Addresses containing register changes.
methods.name: getRegisterAddressSet
methods.comment: Returns the set of Addresses containing register changes.
